name: DAT - MindRelaxer - Planet MSX93
description: Far away planets were a common travel destination within the DAT Afterlife Social Platform. Digitized souls used to explore the impossible canyons of MSX93 and the bio luminescent swamps of ZX91.  After the Collapse of DAT, a few hundreds souls got stuck on those aliens lands, unable to return to their main hub, and yet finding a temporary shelter from the corrupting data set. Discover more at dat.rubenfro.com - RubenFro - Twitter: @Ruben_Fro
